{"tid":158994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港有得賣】高潔絲M巾有活蟲？ 江蘇女：賠10包邊敢用","createTime":"2017-03-16T16:13:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T14:58:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e6afa745b0f7dd15ac5dbb673045facac7a81da6","tid":158994,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T16:13:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56425902&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170315\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56425902%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170315&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK68n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=17e21c0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56425902%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170315&h=082c4a22\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56425902&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170315</a>\t<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170314/large/1489477624_4bbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170314%2Flarge%2F1489477624_4bbe.jpg&h=2720e671&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n江蘇南通一名彭姓女子，近日購買香港也有出售的高潔絲(Kotex)衞生巾，打開使用時竟然發現衞生巾裏爬出活蟲，嚇得她花容失色。<br />\n<br />\n彭女表示，她買了一包高潔絲衞生巾後，因為沒用完就用膠袋包好存放起來，當她再次拿出來準備使用時，居然發現有活蟲從衞生巾邊緣的小圓孔爬了出來。她說：「很惡心，我當時都要吐了，一天都沒有吃飯」。<br />\n<br />\n她隨後致電售後服務，客服一直沒有解決問題，只說「以一賠十」賠償衞生巾，但這樣質素的衞生巾，彭女已不敢使用。她要求客服賠償，以及安排一次身體檢查。內地代理高潔絲衞生巾的金佰利公司公關經理表示，由於衞生巾產品是在高溫高壓的環境下生產，是不太可能出現活蟲或蟲卵的，已經跟消費者溝通，她下周會將衞生巾拿過來，公司會將產品由專業機構檢測，有檢測結果後將會通知她，然後下一步才按照相關規定處理。"},{"pid":"d73751797c47a44830b7c4c441755d9a28bfd4d1","tid":158994,"uid":8514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:06:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港有得賣 所以佢係江蘇買定係係香港買"},{"pid":"e2d30d670ad401bd7045e6ac7bb18a8541ada28b","tid":158994,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-16T18:13:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08f6a96349076a06605fd8387a78617aaf5225d7","tid":158994,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba884423c019659bdca7b1c5754ee73eaa7351d","tid":158994,"uid":43705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:39:49.000Z","msg":"佢個膠袋本身有？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0672c4c9c16308056f506aa9c815e14da2c0baf","tid":158994,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"睇清楚係咪正貨呀，鄰國有D假貨個名好似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cfe7360bc6781fc4c899f6589ba4dd3d2a91e58","tid":158994,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:58:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}